*ventrilo-server-bin-2.3.1 (19 Nov 2005)

  19 Nov 2005; <chainsaw@gentoo.org> +ventrilo-server-bin-2.3.1.ebuild:
  Security version bump with stable keywords for denial of service
  vulnerability, closes bug #111955.

  30 Nov 2004; Sven Wegener <swegener@gentoo.org>
  ventrilo-server-bin-2.2.0-r1.ebuild, ventrilo-server-bin-2.2.0.ebuild:
  Fixed invalid atoms in *DEPEND.

  03 Sep 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  ventrilo-server-bin-2.2.0-r1.ebuild:
  Stable amd64, x86.

